                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d6">
                        <locus target="#140v">Fol. 140v: </locus>
                        <desc>The donor Tawalda Madḫǝn with mamhǝr Takla Libānos and
                           soldiers.</desc>Legend in the upper left margin: መምህር፡ ተክለ፡ ሊባኖስ, “Mämhǝr
