                        ፍቁራኒሁ፡ ባህር፡ ነጋሢ፡ ተወልደ፡ መድኅን, “How bāhr nagāśi Tawalda Madḫǝn is conversing
                        with his beloved ones”.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d7">
                        <locus target="#141r">Fol. 141r: </locus>
                        <desc>The donor Tawalda Madḫǝn, guided by the Angel, and his
